thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Andrew

author: Andrew
title: Andrew
text: As I have been fortunate enough to never ever having to make a claim in 30 years of travelling I cannot, with all honesty, give an in depth review of The Fast Cover Travel Insurance Company. However I do know that it is one of the easiest and quickest ways of obtaining travel Insurance that I have ever used.
